{"tid":2491971,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"菲臘親王呢條能樣，死左都要係度阻撚住曬，煩唔煩啲呀？","createTime":"2021-04-16T16:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T22:48:08.000Z","uid":343520,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6b958fd269a908f311fa0af54f2829d4a7cfe6fe","tid":2491971,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"桌球世錦賽將於周六（17日）在謝菲爾德克魯斯堡劇院展開，世巡賽官網宣布當日賽事將為剛去世的菲臘親王中途暫停，並且默哀一分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n英國白金漢宮公布已菲臘親王周六在溫莎堡的葬禮安排，儀式在下午3點開始，而世錦賽的賽程上，有兩場首輪賽事（2點半開始）屆時會暫停，在場球員，裁判及球迷等會進行一分鐘默哀，當場的四位球員及兩位裁判都會戴上黑色臂章。賽會表示這是世錦賽94年來，首次會中途暫停比賽，並進行默哀儀式，藉此對菲臘親王的最後致敬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">屌你老母好心有啲人死就死啦，係都要全世界關心佢先開心嘅，呢啲陷家剷阻住地球轉，咁大個人仲學人玩情緒勒索，食屎狗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8ab8902f3dc8456fcbd137b30e013e1a9d4fbd","tid":2491971,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T17:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27442fea87dd958b77def6aa8ac1e3d30978494f","tid":2491971,"uid":393512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T17:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619f8bc5383f92f34ce3dd0de873f582a4d1f5b7","tid":2491971,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T17:06:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老母連登成班傻閪哭曬喪咁嘔唔嘔心啲？<br />\n<br />\n菲臘親王全名係乜你分分鐘都唔知啦，on99"},{"pid":"4fa625e2bca7967aae05b369a5648715a1cd637b","tid":2491971,"uid":106001,"like":3,